{"comments":"Message Algebra for Product Tours\n\nThis module provides the complete message vocabulary for tour events.\nAll possible tour actions are represented as a bounded ADT, enabling:\n- Complete pattern matching (no missing cases)\n- Deterministic behavior\n- Serializable event log\n\n## Architecture\n\nThe tour follows the Elm architecture:\n```\nState × Msg → State × [Cmd]\nview :: State → Element Msg\n```\n\nAll messages are pure data. Side effects are expressed as Cmd values\nthat the runtime interprets.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Tour.Msg as Msg\n\nhandleMsg :: Msg.TourMsg MyAppMsg -> AppState -> { state :: AppState, cmds :: Array Cmd }\nhandleMsg msg state = case msg of\n  Msg.NextStep -> advanceToNextStep state\n  Msg.PrevStep -> goToPrevStep state\n  Msg.CustomAction appMsg -> handleAppMsg appMsg state\n  ...\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Tour","Msg"],"LifecycleMsg"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[91,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Tour/Msg.purs","start":[91,3]},"title":"Lifecycle"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Tour","Msg"],"NavigationMsg"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[95,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Tour/Msg.purs","start":[95,3]},"title":"Navigation"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Tour","Msg"],"TargetMsg"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[99,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Tour/Msg.purs","start":[99,3]},"title":"Target"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Tour","Msg"],"AnimationMsg"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[103,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Tour/Msg.purs","start":[103,3]},"title